reviews.productTitle: Leviton 5603-2AW Antimicrobial 15 Amp 120/277V Decora Rocker 3-Way AC Quiet Switch, White
reviews.text: Leviton has quickly become my go to for switches and outlets. Their quality, color, durability and performance places them atop the competition. These switches are awesome! Nice satisfying click, larger surface area and great neutral white color. I find the decora style give a nice modern touch. They are also easier to configure into 2 gang and 3 gang applications. The decora wall plate gives option for light switches, outlets, pass through bristles and fan switches. No more counting wall plates and ending up with a pile of extras. You get just one style of wall plate for your whole project! This is a great option, especially for people adding smart switches to their home.
reviews.date: Reviewed in the United States on October 16, 2022
reviews.title: Less cowbell, more decora

reviews.productTitle: Leviton 5603-2AW Antimicrobial 15 Amp 120/277V Decora Rocker 3-Way AC Quiet Switch, White
reviews.text: I replaced my old 3-way switches with these Decora style switches. However the three screws to tie down the power wires are in a different layout then the old switch, and my wires were not coded to let me know which wire was the hot, and which was the traveler to the other switch, so I had to guess. It took two tries to get it right. Fortunately, as my electrician brother told me later, there was no danger of blowing myself up... the switches would either work, half work, or not work at all depending on where the wires were attached.
